originalText.text: I pay monthly to park here but my my car is never there when requested via app or text. The staff treats us like we park there for free and by staff I mean every single attendant there including manager has been rude, impolite, and inattentive. Convenience is expensive here.

originalText.text: My husband and I figured out that they were taking our car out when we weren't using it. We took pictures of the miles when we dropped it off and then when we took the car out again and it was 40-70 miles over.  Items in the console were out of place and the seat positions were changed. Avoid his place at all costs.
